text: 1. WHA PRESS GUIDANCE, AUGUST 23, 2004:
label: HH1

text: -- VENEZUELA: FINAL COMMENT ON REFERENDUM RESULTS --
label: HH3

text: Q: WHAT IS THE U.S. REACTION TO THE INTERNATIONAL
label: BODY

text: OBSERVERS, ANNOUNCEMENT THAT THEIR PARTIAL AUDIT CONFIRMED
label: HH2

text: PRESIDENT CHAVEZ, VICTORY IN THE REFERENDUM?
label: HH2

text: A: THE RESULTS OF THE OAS AND CARTER CENTER AUDIT ARE
label: HH1

text: CONSISTENT WITH THE RESULTS ANNOUNCED BY THE NATIONAL
label: HH2

text: ELECTORAL COUNCIL ON AUGUST 16. WE UNDERSTAND THE ELECTORAL
label: BODY

text: COUNCIL WILL CERTIFY THE FINAL RESULTS ON AUGUST 25.
label: HH2

text: WE URGE THE INTERNATIONAL COMMUNITY, LED BY THE OAS AND THE
label: HH3

text: FRIENDS OF THE OAS SECRETARY GENERAL FOR VENEZUELA AND THE
label: HH2

text: CARTER CENTER, TO CONTINUE TO SUPPORT THE VENEZUELAN
label: HH2

text: PEOPLE,S DEMOCRATIC EFFORTS.
label: HH2

text: Q: DOES THIS MEAN THE U.S. NOW ACCEPTS CHAVEZ, VICTORY IN
label: HH1

text: THE REFERENDUM?
label: HH2

text: A: WE RECOGNIZE THE INTERNATIONAL OBSERVERS, FINDINGS ARE
label: HH1

text: CONSISTANT WITH THE RESULTS OF THE NATIONAL ELECTORAL COUNCIL.
label: HH2

text: THE RESULTS SPEAK FOR THEMSELVES.
label: HH3

text: Q: WHAT ABOUT CONTINUED OPPOSITION ALLEGATIONS OF FRAUD?
label: HH1

text: REFUSAL TO ACCEPT THE RESULTS?
label: HH2

text: A: WE NOTE THE CONCERNS RAISED BY THE OPPOSITION.
label: BODY

text: WE URGE THE DEMOCRATIC OPPOSITION TO HEED SECRETARY GENERAL
label: HH3

text: GAVIRIA,S OFFER TO PRESENT ANY EVIDENCE OF POSSIBLE FRAUD TO
label: HH2

text: THE OAS.
label: BODY

text: THROUGHOUT THIS PROCESS, WE HAVE EXPRESSED CONCERN ABOUT
label: HH3

text: INTIMIDATION OF CIVIC ORGANIZATIONS SUCH AS THE SUMATE (PRON.
label: HH2

text: SU-MA-TAY), THE POLITIZATION OF STATE INSTITUTIONS AND THE
label: HH2

text: USE OF THE JUDICIARY FOR POLITICAL MEANS.
label: HH2

text: WE REMAIN CONCERNED THAT DOUBTS ABOUT THE PROCESS MAY
label: HH3

text: EXACERBATE POLARIZATION IN VENEZUELA.
label: HH2

text: UNCLASSIFIED
label: H3

text: UNCLASSIFIED
label: H3

text: WE URGE BOTH THE VENEZUELAN GOVERNMENT AND THE DEMOCRATIC
label: HH3

text: OPPOSITION TO WORK TOWARD REDUCING THESE TENSIONS AND TO
label: HH2

text: ENGAGE IN A CONSTRUCTIVE DEMOCRATIC DIALOGUE.
label: BODY

text: THE VENEZUELAN GOVERNMENT HAS THE SPECIAL RESPONSIBILITY OF
label: HH3

text: GUARANTEEING THE RIGHTS OF ALL CITIZENS. THE OPPOSITION HAS
label: HH2

text: THE DUTY TO EXPRESS ITS CONCERNS RESPONSIBLY AND PEACEFULLY.
label: HH2

text: IF ASKED:
label: HH3

text: Q: REACTION TO PRESIDENT CHAVEZ, COMMENTS OVER THE WEEKEND
label: HH1

text: THAT HE REFUSED TO ACKNOWLEDGE THE OPPOSITION?
label: HH2

text: A: WE BELIEVE SUCH COMMENTS ARE NOT CONDUCIVE TO NATIONAL
label: HH1

text: PEACE AND DEMOCRATIC ENGAGEMENT. WE CALL ON ALL PARTIES TO
label: HH2

text: REFRAIN FROM IRRESPONSIBLE RHETORIC AND ACTIONS, WHICH ONLY
label: HH2

text: SERVE TO DEEPEN THE POLARIZATION.
label: HH2

text: 2. WHA PRESS GUIDANCE, AUGUST 24, 2004:
label: HH1

text: -- CUBA ) COMMISSION FOR ASSISTANCE TO A FREE CUBA:
label: HH3

text: WASHINGTON POST ARTICLE ON AUGUST 24, 2004 --
label: BODY

text: Q. HOW DO YOU RESPOND TO THE CHARGE THAT OUR CUBA POLICY IS
label: HH1

text: POLITICALLY MOTIVATED?
label: HH2

text: A: OUR POLICY TOWARD CUBA IS TO ENCOURAGE A RAPID, PEACEFUL
label: BODY

text: TRANSITION TO DEMOCRACY. TO HELP THE CUBAN PEOPLE ACHIEVE
label: HH2

text: THIS GOAL, THE PRESIDENT CREATED THE COMMISSION FOR
label: HH2

text: ASSISTANCE TO A FREE CUBA WITH A MANDATE TO HELP BRING AN END
label: HH2

text: TO THE DICTATORSHIP, AND TO LAY OUT A PLAN FOR ASSISTANCE TO
label: BODY

text: A FREE CUBA.
label: BODY

text: THE COMMISSION RECOMMENDED AN INTEGRATED, STRATEGIC APPROACH
label: HH3

text: TO SUPPORT THE DEVELOPMENT OF CIVIL SOCIETY IN CUBA AND LIMIT
label: HH2

text: THE REGIMES MANIPULATION OF HUMANITARIAN POLICIES TO
label: HH2

text: ACCUMULATE RESOURCES TO FINANCE REPRESSION. THE
label: HH2

text: COMMISSION,S RECOMMENDATIONS ARE BEING IMPLEMENTED.
label: HH2

text: Q. HOW DO YOU RESPOND TO CHARGES THAT THE POLICY IS TOO
label: HH1

text: HARSH AND HAS ALIENATED CUBAN-AMERICANS?
label: HH2

text: A: THE CHANGES IN LICENSING RULES ARE DESIGNED TO LIMIT THE
label: HH1

text: FLOW OF U.S. DOLLARS TO THE CASTRO REGIME AND ARE NOT
label: HH2

text: DIRECTED SOLELY AT CUBAN-AMERICANS.
label: HH2

text: THE COMMISSION RECOMMENDED CHANGES THAT INCLUDED TIGHTENING
label: HH3

text: UNCLASSIFIED
label: H3

text: UNCLASSIFIED
label: H3

text: OF RESTRICTIONS ON EDUCATIONAL AND PROFESSIONAL ACTIVITIES IN
label: HH2

text: CUBA, AS WELL AS LIMITING FAMILY TRAVEL. THE COMMISSION ALSO
label: HH2

text: WELCOMED COMMENTS FROM INDIVIDUALS AND ORGANIZATIONS,
label: HH2

text: REVIEWED HUNDREDS OF E-MAILS AND LETTERS, AND MET WITH A
label: HH2

text: DIVERSE GROUP OF EXPERTS, WHOSE OPINIONS SPANNED A RANGE OF
label: HH2

text: VIEWS FROM THE CUBAN-AMERICAN COMMUNITY.
label: HH2

text: Q. WHAT RULES ARE CURRENTLY IN PLACE REGARDING FOOD,
label: HH1

text: MEDICINE AND TOILETRIES TO CUBA?
label: HH2

text: A: THE COMMISSION DETERMINED THAT THE CUBAN GOVERNMENT
label: HH1

text: EARNED TENS OF MILLIONS OF DOLLARS ANNUALLY BY CHARGING
label: HH2

text: DELIVERY FEES TO RECIPIENTS OF GIFT PARCELS. RECOGNIZING
label: HH2

text: THAT GIFT PARCELS MEET A FUNDAMENTAL HUMANITARIAN NEED IN
label: HH2

text: CUBA, THE COMMISSION RECOMMENDED THAT GIFT PARCELS BE LIMITED
label: HH2

text: TO FOOD, MEDICINES, MEDICAL SUPPLIES AND DEVICES, RADIOS AND
label: HH2

text: BATTERIES. THIS RECOMMENDATION HAS BEEN IMPLEMENTED.
label: HH2

text: FOR ADDITIONAL INFORMATION ON GIFT PARCELS, I SUGGEST THAT
label: HH3

text: YOU CONTACT THE DEPARTMENT OF COMMERCE.
label: HH2

text: Q. IS THERE A REVIEW OF IMPLEMENTATION UNDERWAY?
label: HH1

text: A: THE NEW TREASURY DEPARTMENT REGULATIONS WERE OPEN FOR
label: HH1

text: PUBLIC COMMENT THROUGH AUGUST 15. WE UNDERSTAND THAT THE
label: HH2

text: TREASURY DEPARTMENT RECEIVED MANY COMMENTS AND WILL BE
label: HH2

text: REVIEWING THEM IN THE COMING MONTHS.
label: HH2

text: WE CONTINUE TO REVIEW OUR POLICIES TO ENSURE THAT WE FULFILL
label: HH3

text: THE RECOMMENDATIONS IN THE COMMISSION,S REPORT TO THE
label: HH2

text: PRESIDENT.
label: BODY

text: -- CUBA: AIRBORNE BROADCASTS OF RADIO AND TV MARTI TO CUBA --
label: HH3

text: (REVISED)
label: BODY

text: Q: COULD YOU GIVE US SOME BACKGROUND ON THE RECENT AIRBORNE
label: HH1

text: BROADCASTS TO CUBA?
label: BODY

text: A: THE COMMISSION FOR ASSISTANCE TO A FREE CUBA RECOMMENDED
label: HH1

text: TO THE PRESIDENT THAT AIRBORNE TRANSMISSIONS OF RADIO AND TV
label: HH2

text: MARTI BROADCASTING BE CARRIED OUT ON A REGULAR BASIS TO BREAK
label: HH2

text: THE CUBAN REGIME'S INFORMATION BLOCKADE ON THE CUBAN PEOPLE.
label: HH2

text: THAT TASK, PART OF AN INTEGRATED APPROACH TO ASSIST THE CUBAN
label: HH3

text: PEOPLE IN THEIR EFFORTS TO BRING ABOUT RAPID AND PEACEFUL
label: HH2

text: CHANGE TO CUBA, WAS BEGUN ON SATURDAY, AUGUST 21. FOR
label: HH2

text: SEVERAL HOURS, A PENNSYLVANIA AIR NATIONAL GUARD AIRCRAFT
label: HH2

text: OPERATING WITHIN U.S. AIRSPACE BROADCAST A RADIO AND TV MARTI
label: HH2

text: SIGNAL CAPABLE OF BEING RECEIVED IN CUBA.
label: HH2

text: UNCLASSIFIED
label: H3

text: UNCLASSIFIED
label: H3

text: BUILDING ON THE EFFORTS OF CUBAN CIVIL SOCIETY, THESE TYPES
label: HH3

text: OF BROADCASTS WILL INCREASE THE AVAILABILITY TO THE CUBAN
label: HH2

text: PEOPLE OF RELIABLE INFORMATION ON EVENTS IN CUBA AND AROUND
label: HH2

text: THE WORLD.
label: BODY

text: Q: DID THE BROADCAST INTERFERE WITH PRIVATE U.S.
label: HH1

text: BROADCASTING?
label: BODY

text: A: THE AIRBORNE BROADCAST OF TV MARTI WAS UNDERTAKEN ON A
label: BODY

text: FREQUENCY ALREADY AUTHORIZED BY THE FEDERAL COMMUNICATIONS
label: HH2

text: COMMISSION FOR TV MARTI BROADCASTS.
label: HH2

text: WE UNDERSTAND THAT RADIO MARTI WAS BROADCAST ON A FREQUENCY
label: HH3

text: NOT USED BY U.S. COMMERCIAL BROADCASTERS.
label: HH2

text: THE FEDERAL COMMUNICATIONS COMMISSION IS TAKING STEPS TO
label: HH3

text: MINIMIZE POTENTIAL TV MARTI INTERFERENCE WITH DOMESTIC
label: HH2

text: STATIONS BY EVALUATING THE IMPACT OF THE BROADCASTS ON
label: HH2

text: DOMESTIC LICENSEES.
label: HH2

text: Q: IS THE DEPARTMENT OF DEFENSE CONCERNED ABOUT POSSIBLE
label: BODY

text: HOSTILE ACTION AGAINST U.S. PERSONNEL IN RESPONSE TO THE
label: HH2

text: BROADCASTS? WHAT WOULD THE RESPONSE TO SUCH AN ACT BE?
label: HH2

text: A: FOR THE SAFETY OF OUR PEOPLE AND OPERATIONAL SECURITY, WE
label: HH1

text: DO NOT DISCUSS OPERATIONAL MATTERS IN DETAIL. HOWEVER,
label: HH2

text: PRECAUTIONS HAVE BEEN TAKEN TO MINIMIZE THE THREATS TO U.S.
label: HH2

text: PERSONNEL FROM CUBAN FIGHTER AIRCRAFT INTERCEPTS OR OTHER
label: HH2

text: DIRECT THREATS AGAINST THE AIRCRAFT.
label: HH2

text: THESE BROADCASTS WERE MADE ONLY IN U.S. AIRSPACE. ANY
label: HH1

text: ATTEMPT TO INTERCEPT THE AIRCRAFT WOULD BE TREATED AS A
label: HH1

text: HOSTILE ACT AND APPROPRIATE SELF-DEFENSE MEASURES WOULD BE
label: HH2

text: TAKEN.
label: BODY

text: Q: CASTRO HAS LONG CLAIMED THAT THE U.S. INTENDS TO TAKE
label: HH1

text: MILITARY ACTION AGAINST CUBA. IS THIS THE FIRST STEP IN THAT
label: HH2

text: PROCESS?
label: BODY

text: A: THE POLICY OF THE UNITED STATES IS TO HASTEN A PEACEFUL
label: BODY

text: TRANSITION TO DEMOCRACY IN CUBA. THAT POLICY HAS BEEN
label: HH2

text: ARTICULATED AT THE HIGHEST LEVELS OF OUR GOVERNMENT,
label: HH2

text: INCLUDING BY SECRETARY POWELL.
label: HH2

text: TV MARTI HAS TRANSMITTED ITS SIGNAL TO CUBA FOR OVER A
label: HH3

text: DECADE, AND ITS SIGNAL IS ROUTINELY JAMMED BY THE REGIME.
label: HH2

text: OUR HOPE IS THAT THESE BROADCASTS WILL ENABLE THE CUBAN
label: HH2

text: PEOPLE TO HAVE ACCESS TO UNCENSORED INFORMATION ABOUT CUBA
label: HH2

text: AND THE WORLD.
label: HH2

text: UNCLASSIFIED
label: H3

text: Q: HAVE YOU RECEIVED ANY PROTESTS FROM THE CUBAN GOVERNMENT
label: HH1

text: CONCERNING THESE BROADCASTS?
label: HH2

text: A: THE CUBAN GOVERNMENT HAS COMPLAINED ABOUT RADIO AND TV
label: HH1

text: MARTI BROADCASTS SINCE THEIR INCEPTION. WE HAVE NO DOUBT
label: HH1

text: THAT THE REGIME WILL CONTINUE TO COMPLAIN ABOUT OUR EFFORTS
label: HH2

text: TO PROVIDE DETAILED AND ACCURATE INFORMATION TO THE CUBAN
label: HH2

text: PEOPLE ABOUT EVENTS OUTSIDE OF CUBA.
label: HH2

text: IT IS OUR POSITION THAT THE MORE CUBANS KNOW ABOUT THE WORLD
label: HH3

text: -- AND THE WORLD KNOWS THE TRUTH ABOUT CUBA -- THE BETTER THE
label: HH2

text: CHANCES OF A RAPID AND PEACEFUL TRANSITION TO DEMOCRACY,
label: BODY

text: WHICH IS THE CENTRAL GOAL OF THE UNITED STATES AND ITS ALLIES
label: HH2
